sentence: In early trading on Monday, shares of Intel ( INTC ) topped the list of the day's best performing Dow Jones Industrial Average components, trading up 1.5%.
Year to date, Intel has lost about 7.2% of its value.
And the worst performing Dow component thus far on the day is DuPont ( DD ), trading down 1.5%.
DuPont is lower by about 9.5% looking at the year to date performance.
Two other components making moves today are UnitedHealth Group ( UNH ), trading down 1.1%, and Home Depot ( HD ), trading up 1.1% on the day.
